{"tid":1491873,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"班狗又出新招","createTime":"2019-08-20T14:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T02:42:16.000Z","uid":258190,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7609c0ae7e08c3ca6d63c27d8b709b70054399d5","tid":1491873,"uid":258190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:59:43.000Z","msg":"班狗又出新招<br />\n受催淚彈影響可索償<br />\n實質呢其實就係想商戶申請<br />\n到時肯定問商戶拿CCTV來做證明你係受影響<br />\n跟住呢就可以順手拉人<br />\n簡單d講姐係用錢收買商人<br />\n旺角 深水埗區最多見錢開眼既人<br />\n而大部分商戶門口必有cctv<br />\n<br />\n你可能會話點解唔直接去商戶拿<br />\n因為唔係個個願意比<br />\n或者覺得怕麻煩<br />\n但依加依個方法可以令佢地有藉口收錢<br />\n仲可以秘密執行<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有開鋪既朋友就勸下佢哋唔好出賣大家"},{"pid":"9de9407f955a8453b7fd89cc2d2c65db039feeac","tid":1491873,"uid":258190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:00:48.000Z","msg":"自推20次"},{"pid":"6b8eb2e4af16f35049d977cb0b1d7a41f2784790","tid":1491873,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:05:46.000Z","msg":"幾有道理"},{"pid":"e9ca95777f022745e280676bd662c579b7f27f15","tid":1491873,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"721 811<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a4772edfae6aecf524d95d76ac424784dc94c1","tid":1491873,"uid":258190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2ef7a904c015a495a5cd7738118f0f3cd502dd0f","tid":1491873,"uid":258190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:07:43.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"5b30260f88204022967b16db022a58a045e2d8b4","tid":1491873,"uid":258190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:08:09.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"5b34991fc2f78398be22eb799648fc111a472d74","tid":1491873,"uid":258190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:13:51.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"06405930341750a5c2a94d9b87203bf5e9deca4a","tid":1491873,"uid":235374,